            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Bedaio <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>et Alounis <note>sic</note> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>sacr</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Catius <lb n="5"/>Secundia<lb break="no" n="6"/>nus IIvir <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratore</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Antonin</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>II et Sacerdote co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Profil von Basis und Corona abgeschlagen. Zierleiste. Datierung erfolgt aufgrund der Nennung der Konsuln.</p>
            </div>
